## Let netd being able to look for the files/directories of which secontext is "shell", normally the custom hosts file in /data/adb/, for example, bind mounting from /data/adb/hosts to /system/etc/hosts
allow netd adb_data_file dir {search}

## Let zygote being able to look for the apk files, normally when bind mounting apk from inside /data/adb/
allow zygote apk_data_file dir {search}

## Let zygote being able to look for the files/directories of which secontext is "shell", normally files/directories in /data/local/tmp/
allow zygote shell_data_file dir {search}

